                <h1>The Brilliant Hermione Granger: A True Role Model</h1>
                <p>Hermione Granger, one of the brightest witches of her age, is a key character in J.K. Rowling's Harry Potter series. Known for her intelligence, resourcefulness, and unwavering loyalty to her friends, Hermione often takes the lead in solving challenges. Her dedication to learning and justice makes her an inspiring role model for readers.</p>
